maintext:
ROCKY HILL, Conn. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday evening’s drawing of the Connecticut Lottery’s “Lucky Links Night” game were:
01-08-09-11-15-16-19-22
(one, eight, nine, eleven, fifteen, sixteen, nineteen, twenty-two)
